<h1>SAFETY AND SECURITY</h1>
<font face="arial"
</font>
<h2><u>Health issues and prevention</u></h2>
<font face="helvetica">
<h3><em>A health issue is something caused by extensive or improper use of computers</em></h3>
</font>
<font face="arial">
<h4><mark> What are the different health issues caused by computer use? </mark></h4>
<p>The health issues include: <strong>back pain</strong> caused by poor posture, <strong>headache</strong> and <strong>eye strain</strong> caused by staring at screen for long time and <strong>RSI in wrists</strong> because of repetitive clicking of mouse.</p>
<style>
