</style>
<img src="https://elearningindustry.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/3-common-elearning-health-issues-and-how-to-overcome-them-1.jpg" id="image" alt="stressed girl"
 width="430" height="250">
<h4><mark>What are the different safety issues caused by computer use?</mark></h4>
<p>The safety issues include tripping over wires lying around, fire from overloaded sockets, heavy equipment falling and causing injury, electrocution from loose/open/wet wires.</p>
</font>
<img src="https://www.explainingcomputers.com/images/ec_dse_1200.jpg" id="image" width=450 height=400>
