<font face="arial">
<h2><mark>HOW CAN THESE BE PREVENTED?</mark></h2>
<p><strong>health</strong></p>
<ol> 
- ergonomic mouse/chair <br>
- regular breaks<br>
- screen filter
</ol>
<p><strong>safety</strong></p>
<ol>
- dont keep heavy equiment close to edge of table<br>
- dont overload sockets/have co2 extinguiser<br>
- insulate wires<br>
- put wires under carpets/in ducts etc
</ol>
